Package interfaces.services

Interface DataServiceable

All Superinterfaces:
Exportable, Importable
All Known Implementing Classes:
CampDataService, CommitteeDataService, StaffDataService, StudentDataService
public interface DataServiceable extends Importable, Exportable
The DataServiceable interface combines functionalities related to data handling, including importing and exporting data.

Classes that implement this interface should provide their own implementations for importing and exporting data as needed for the specific application.
